  "description": "A better model and texture for the enchanting table",
  "body": "[![Modrinth - My other projects](https://img.shields.io/badge/modrinth-My_other_projects-00AF5C?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth)](https://modrinth.com/user/Jacosvaldo)\n[![Discord - Jacosvaldo's Not Too Cool Server](https://img.shields.io/badge/Discord-Jacosvaldo%27s%20_Not_Too_Cool_Server-5865F2?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord)](https://discord.com/invite/cPYyf3JqgU)\n[![Kofi - Tip me](https://img.shields.io/badge/kofi-Tip_me-F26B2E?style=for-the-badge&logo=kofi)](https://ko-fi.com/jacosvaldo)\n\n---\n\n## ✨ Better Model and Texture!!!\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/d9PIjVLE/8a5391f0142c470b10abb1c6df2fd3e7233a03d9.png\" width=\"320\" alt=\"Better Enchanting Table preview\">\n\n---\n\n## 🎨 Color Variants\n![Yellow, green, red and purple color variants](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/d9PIjVLE/images/c2ae418144c6f3d5e10701dea742f0b2775d01d8.png)\n\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"font-size:1.3em; font-weight:bold;\">Check the gallery for more samples!!!</p>\n\n---\n\n## 🧩 Dependencies\n\nNo mod is actually required, but **OptiFine** or [Continuity](https://modrinth.com/mod/continuity) are needed to enable emissive (glowing) textures.\n\n![Enchanting table emissive example](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/d9PIjVLE/images/df31a1047078a1a5c7b05780f265b3f2702dc70b.png)\n\n---\n\n## 💡 Tips & Compatibility\n\n✅ Works perfectly with [Enchanting Table Magic Circle](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/enchanting-table-magic-circle)\n  \n  ![Compatibility example](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/d9PIjVLE/images/b2743fe7172b43dc457a6715e5644d4079af86a5.png)\n\n💠 Prefer a simpler version? Try [Vanilla Better Enchanting Table](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/vanilla-better-enchanting-table)\n  \n  ![Simpler version preview](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/uE1RvdVA/images/07711e911b82b4db241ba4caaa742aee1997acf9.gif)\n\n---\n\n## 💼 My works\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/connected-paths\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Nyfj98b5/images/d2f6fe5c972e45223b8cf11208ffffeb83e41dda.png\" alt=\"Connected Paths\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/connected-rocks\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/IE9kFeq9/images/5bf749f3cb7aaadbea0f7d466e778caad31ede30.png\" alt=\"Connected Rocks\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/connected-bricks\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/mnKF5Qd2/images/661274f70b3404470a9a6097f138a09f1c09bd2e.png\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/void-dragon\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/2mCxIlku/images/669e421ccdfbcbc3b89ab705976712e53500a1c0.png\" alt=\"Void Dragon\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-lanterns\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/n09olmOJ/images/ee19a80fb28a236ca9f25fb294172b400ef336fb.png\" alt=\"Emissive Lanterns\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/enchanting-table-magic-circle\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f4838d8cfdbd75d3cca8bb063cab8e3d154107e5.png\" alt=\"Enchanting Table Magic Circle\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/better-enchanting-table\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/d9PIjVLE/images/3c67b63c7e5a4be75edaa9f05a0f10b66b3bf75d.png\" alt=\"Better Enchanting Table\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/vanilla-better-enchanting-table\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/uE1RvdVA/images/0ddf81551efb39604028c735fc619393f591f17a.png\" alt=\"Vanilla Better Enchanting Table\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/fast-better-grass-for-simple-grass-flowers\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/pOumd1F9/images/86315d23cee01bdef72d659243e9ef907ec97792.png\" alt=\"Fast Better Grass For Simple Grass Flowers\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/better-lily-pads_\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/64TlNiYG/images/05a52d02b3e57e9037838fa1826d1c74249c0a25.png\" alt=\"Better Lily Pads\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/vanilla-better-lily-pads\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/CnUjp8e3/images/f3e079e5f3ee6f28b357e83370096997ad580cca.png\" alt=\"Vanilla Better Lily Pads\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/vanilla-bushy-leaves\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/JKvJahJC/images/fa6dc4969d6f61c5d4e4727fd06e9bdee08ec1e3.png\" alt=\"Vanilla Bushy Leaves\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/modpack/sweeter-vanilla\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Qgy3TXWA/images/63736f4117ba3647291de6bec87f0578eb18232f.png\" alt=\"Sweeter Vanilla\" width=\"204\"> </a>\n\n[![Use code JACOS for 25% discount at Sparked Host servers](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c027e7de8616ac177d4267980d53eaacfa9e2022_0.webp)](https://billing.sparkedhost.com/aff.php?aff=3074)",
